   • → Windows/dirs/Windows/CSC[`CSC`]
   • → Windows/dirs/Windows/Downloaded-Program-Files[`Downloaded Program Files`]
   • → Windows/dirs/Windows/Fonts[`Fonts`]
   • → Windows/dirs/Windows/INF[`INF`]
   • → Windows/dirs/Windows/Installer[`Installer`]
